<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Someone commented on a topic created by you.</h1>
    <p>
      <%= link_to @comment.user.name, user_url(@comment.user) %> commented on your topic "<%= link_to @comment.topic.title, topic_url(@comment.topic) %>" at <%= l @comment.created_at, :format => :long %>.<br />
      The comment: <%= @comment.text %><br />
      <%= link_to "View in context", topic_url(@comment.topic) + "#c#{ @comment.id }" %>
    </p>
    <p>You can disable these notifications in your <%= link_to "user options", edit_user_url %>.</p>
    <p><%= link_to "Agora", root_url %>, 2012.</p>
  </body>
</html>
